.TH UNPDF 1 "July 2026" "unpdf" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
unpdf \- convert PDF documents to HTML
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B unpdf
.I input.pdf
.RI [ options ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B unpdf
converts PDF text, links, vector paths, semantic forms, and browser-safe
embedded fonts to semantic or fixed-layout HTML.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR -o ", " --output " " directory
Write generated HTML and assets to the directory.
.TP
.B --force
Write into a non-empty output directory.
.TP
.BR --text-mode " semantic|fixed"
Select semantic or fixed text layout.
.TP
.BR --page-mode " continuous|fixed"
Select continuous flow or fixed PDF pages.
.TP
.BR -q ", " --quiet
Suppress success and warning messages.
.TP
.BR -h ", " --help
Show command help.
.TP
.B --version
Show the version.
.SH HOMEPAGE
https://github.com/erikbra/pdfbox-net
